data.title: About: WEKY
data.meta_description: WEKY (1340 AM) is a radio station broadcasting a classic hits format. Licensed to Richmond, Kentucky, United States, the station serves the Lexington Metro Area. The station is currently owned by Wallingford Communications, LLC and features programming from ABC Radio.

WEKY (1340 AM) is a radio station broadcasting a classic hits format. Licensed to Richmond, Kentucky, United States, the station serves the Lexington Metro Area. The station is currently owned by Wallingford Communications, LLC and features programming from ABC Radio. (en)
